        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 16:07:39 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 16:07:39 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Rich Johnson, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/07/ai-music-producer-accused-of-bilking-music-streamers-for-millions.webp" alt="AI music producer accused of bilking music streamers for millions" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">AI music producer accused of bilking music streamers for millions</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Michael Smith allegedly used AI to create songs, then bots to continuously stream those songs, creating millions in fraudulent royalties.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/07/ai-music-producer-accused-of-bilking-music-streamers-for-millions/"  >(Rich Johnson, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:00:33 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 16:00:33 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/05/georgia-school-shooting-what-we-know-about-the-victims.webp" alt="Georgia school shooting: What we know about the victims" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Georgia school shooting: What we know about the victims</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      A 14-year-old Georgia high school student has been charged as an adult with using an assault-style rifle to kill two students and two teachers in the hallway outside his algebra classroom, according to authorities.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/05/georgia-school-shooting-what-we-know-about-the-victims/"  >(The Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:43:02 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:43:02 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="LEANNE ITALIE, Associated Press, ABC 4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/06/ralph-lauren-draws-the-fashion-crowd-to-the-horsey-hamptons-for-a-diverse-show-of-americana.webp" alt="Ralph Lauren draws the fashion crowd to the horsey Hamptons for a diverse show of Americana" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Ralph Lauren draws the fashion crowd to the horsey Hamptons for a diverse show of Americana</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      BRIDGEHAMPTON, N.Y. (AP) — Ralph Lauren took to Hamptons horse country for a rollout of his signature Americana featuring first lady Jill Biden, Usher and Colman Domingo on his front row and Naomi Campbell, Christy Turlington and a bevy of adorable kids on his runway.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/06/ralph-lauren-draws-the-fashion-crowd-to-the-horsey-hamptons-for-a-diverse-show-of-americana/"  >(LEANNE ITALIE, Associated Press, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:32:44 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 14:32:44 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, KRON4">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/06/trump-motorcade-arrives-at-appeals-court-in-e-jean-carroll-sex-abuse-case.webp" alt="Trump appears in appeals court in E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" >
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Trump appears in appeals court in E. Jean Carroll sex abuse case</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Veering from the campaign trail to a courtroom, Donald Trump quietly observed Friday as one of his lawyers fought to overturn a verdict finding the former president liable for sexual abuse and defamation.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/06/trump-motorcade-arrives-at-appeals-court-in-e-jean-carroll-sex-abuse-case/"  >(The Associated Press, KRON4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:46:20 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:46:20 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/08/georgia-shooting-suspects-mother-called-apalachee-high-school-warning-extreme-emergency-aunt-says.webp" alt="Georgia shooting suspect's mother called Apalachee High School warning of 'extreme emergency,' aunt says" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Georgia shooting suspect's mother called Apalachee High School warning of 'extreme emergency,' aunt says</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Colt Gray&apos;s mom said she called Apalachee High School fearing an &quot;impending disaster&quot; and begged staff to check on her son due to an &quot;extreme emergency.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/08/georgia-shooting-suspects-mother-called-apalachee-high-school-warning-extreme-emergency-aunt-says/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:43:34 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:43:34 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Jeremy Tanner, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/08/september-tax-filing-deadline-looms-except-in-these-disaster-areas.webp" alt="September tax filing deadline looms &#8211; except in these disaster areas" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">September tax filing deadline looms &#8211; except in these disaster areas</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The September deadline to make an estimated tax payment is fast approaching, but taxpayers living in designated disaster zones across the U.S. will be granted an automatic delay, according to the IRS.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/08/september-tax-filing-deadline-looms-except-in-these-disaster-areas/"  >(Jeremy Tanner, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:45:14 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:45:14 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="The Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/us/2024/09/06/teen-accused-of-killing-4-at-georgia-high-school-to-make-first-court-appearance.webp" alt="Teen suspect in Ga. school shooting and his father to remain held after hearings" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Teen suspect in Ga. school shooting and his father to remain held after hearings</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The 14-year-old suspect in a shooting at a Georgia high school that killed four people and his father will both stay in custody following back-to-back court hearings Friday morning where their lawyers declined to seek bail.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2024/09/06/teen-accused-of-killing-4-at-georgia-high-school-to-make-first-court-appearance/"  >(The Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
