        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Russian 'spy' whale: Groups speculate Hvaldimir was shot</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The animal rights groups allege that preliminary autopsy results suggest Hvaldimir suffered gunshot wounds.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/05/police-report-russian-spy-whale-hvaldimir-was-shot/"  >(Katie Smith, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:52:38 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 09 Sep 2024 01:52:38 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Sarah Fortinsky, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/09/three-israeli-civilians-killed-at-crossing-between-west-bank-and-jordan.webp" alt="Three Israeli civilians killed at crossing between West Bank and Jordan" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Three Israeli civilians killed at crossing between West Bank and Jordan</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Three Israeli civilians were killed on Sunday by a Jordanian gunman who opened fire at the Allenby Crossing connecting the West Bank and Jordan, the Israel Defense Forces (IDF) said in a statement.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/09/three-israeli-civilians-killed-at-crossing-between-west-bank-and-jordan/"  >(Sarah Fortinsky, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 00:23:23 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 00:23:23 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Liz Jassin, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/05/russian-election-interference-wake-up-call-john-kirby.webp" alt="Russian election interference is 'wake-up call': John Kirby" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Russian election interference is 'wake-up call': John Kirby</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      "It's incumbent on Americans to be careful and patient about the news their receiving," Kirby said Wednesday on "Elizabeth Vargas Reports.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/05/russian-election-interference-wake-up-call-john-kirby/"  >(Liz Jassin, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 20:16:01 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 20:16:01 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Tara Suter, The Hill">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/05/claudia-tenney-probe-kathy-hochul-aide.webp" alt="House Republican urges probe into 'full impact' of former Hochul aide's China ties" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">House Republican urges probe into 'full impact' of former Hochul aide's China ties</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Rep. Claudia Tenney (R-N.Y.) pushed for a probe into a former aide for New York Gov. Kathy Hochul (D) and the "the full impact" of her "influence on the New York State government and economy" in the wake of the aide being charged with and arrested for acting as an agent of China.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/05/claudia-tenney-probe-kathy-hochul-aide/"  >(Tara Suter, The Hill)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:25:37 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:25:37 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Connell McShane, NewsNation">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/05/russia-election-interference-tactics-same-goal.webp" alt="Russia's new election interference tactics have same goal: Expert" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Russia's new election interference tactics have same goal: Expert</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Justice Department on Wednesday announced it seized 32 web domains Russia used for covert campaigns.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/05/russia-election-interference-tactics-same-goal/"  >(Connell McShane, NewsNation)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:32:38 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:32:38 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="EVELYNE MUSAMBI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/07/kenyan-officials-remove-bodies-as-they-try-to-confirm-the-death-toll-from-a-school-dormitory-fire.webp" alt="21 children are now known to have died in Kenya school fire" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">21 children are now known to have died in Kenya school fire</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      NAIROBI, Kenya (AP) — The number of children who were burned to death in a school dormitory in central Kenya has risen to 21, the government spokesperson said Saturday. Officials began removing the bodies of the children as they tried to account for dozens of boys who were still missing.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/07/kenyan-officials-remove-bodies-as-they-try-to-confirm-the-death-toll-from-a-school-dormitory-fire/"  >(EVELYNE MUSAMBI, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 19:47:32 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 19:47:32 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, PIX 11">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/world/2024/09/08/nato-member-romania-says-a-russian-drone-violated-its-airspace.webp" alt="Two NATO members say Russian drones violated their airspace" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Two NATO members say Russian drones violated their airspace</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      KYIV, Ukraine (AP) — Two NATO members said Sunday that Russian drones violated their airspace, as one reportedly flew into Romania during nighttime attacks on neighboring Ukraine while another crashed in eastern Latvia the previous day.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/world/2024/09/08/nato-member-romania-says-a-russian-drone-violated-its-airspace/"  >(Associated Press, PIX 11)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
