        <div class="row"><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:00:40 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:00:40 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/tech/2024/09/02/beware-social-security-scam-crooks-trying-trick-you.webp" alt="Beware of this Social Security scam by crooks trying to trick you" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Beware of this Social Security scam by crooks trying to trick you</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      You can never be too prepared: Tech expert Kurt “CyberGuy&quot; Knutsson offers some tips to help you guard against new Social Security scams.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/02/beware-social-security-scam-crooks-trying-trick-you/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
