        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Google faces new antitrust trial after ruling declaring search engine a monopoly</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      One month after a judge declared Google's search engine an illegal monopoly, the tech giant faces another antitrust lawsuit that threatens to break up the company, this time over its advertising technology.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/09/google-faces-new-antitrust-trial-after-ruling-declaring-search-engine-a-monopoly/"  >(MATTHEW BARAKAT, Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
