        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Video game performers reach agreement with 80 video games on AI terms</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      LOS ANGELES (AP) — After striking for over a month, video game performers have reached agreements with 80 games that have signed interim or tiered budget agreements with the performers' union and accepted the artificial intelligence provisions they have been seeking.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/06/video-game-performers-reach-agreement-with-80-video-games-on-ai-terms/"  >(KAITLYN HUAMANI, Associated Press, KLAS, CBS News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
