      Jones said it's just another tool to keep people in the community and first responders safe during emergencies.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/tech/2024/09/05/texas-police-department-using-autonomous-drones-to-respond-to-emergency-calls/"  >(Nabil Remadna, NewsNation)</a>
