  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/08/utes-defense-dominates-rising-injured-in-23-12-victory.webp" alt="Utes defense dominates, Rising injured in 23-12 victory" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Utes defense dominates, Rising injured in 23-12 victory</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      SALT LAKE CITY (ABC4 Sports) - Cam Rising threw for 92 yards and two touchdowns before leaving the game due to an injury to his throwing hand as No. 11 Utah beat Baylor 23-12 on Saturday at Rice-Eccles Stadium.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/08/utes-defense-dominates-rising-injured-in-23-12-victory/"  >(Dana Greene, ABC 4)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:03:35 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:03:35 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Jon Wilner, The Mercury News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/08/best-of-the-west-rankings-utah-on-top-again-as-boise-state-and-cal-rise-arizona-slips-and-colorado-falls.webp" alt="Best of the West rankings: Utah on top (again) as Boise State and Cal rise, Arizona slips and Colorado falls" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Best of the West rankings: Utah on top (again) as Boise State and Cal rise, Arizona slips and Colorado falls</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The Broncos pushed Oregon to the brink, and the Bears won at Auburn. Meanwhile, Arizona dropped a few spots in the latest BOTW.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/08/best-of-the-west-rankings-utah-on-top-again-as-boise-state-and-cal-rise-arizona-slips-and-colorado-falls/"  >(Jon Wilner, The Mercury News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:04:57 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:04:57 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Georgia McCarthur, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/09/tampa-bay-buccaneers-fans-react-to-season-opener-victory-over-commanders.webp" alt="Tampa Bay Buccaneers fans react to season opener victory over Commanders" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Tampa Bay Buccaneers fans react to season opener victory over Commanders</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Tampa Bay Buccaneers fans are celebrating a season opener win on Sunday after defeating the Washington Commanders 37-20. Now, fans hope to keep that momentum going.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/09/tampa-bay-buccaneers-fans-react-to-season-opener-victory-over-commanders/"  >(Georgia McCarthur, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 23:48:38 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 23:48:38 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Associated Press, Fox 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/07/canada-beats-united-states-in-u-s-for-first-time-since-1957-winning-friendly-2-1.webp" alt="Canada beats United States in U.S. for first time since 1957, winning friendly 2-1" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Canada beats United States in U.S. for first time since 1957, winning friendly 2-1</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Hoping to show its first-round exit at the Copa America was a fluke, the United States instead displayed an alarming lack of intensity and an abundant defensive disarray that resulted in its first home loss to Canada since 1957.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/07/canada-beats-united-states-in-u-s-for-first-time-since-1957-winning-friendly-2-1/"  >(Associated Press, Fox 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:32:17 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:32:17 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="ANNE M. PETERSON, Associated Press, KTLA 5">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/05/alex-morgan-retires-from-professional-soccer-and-is-expecting-her-second-child.webp" alt="USWNT star Alex Morgan retires from professional soccer; expecting second child" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">USWNT star Alex Morgan retires from professional soccer; expecting second child</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      With two Women's World Cup titles and an Olympic gold medal, Alex Morgan is retiring from professional soccer as one of the United States national team's most prolific scorers and as someone who helped lead the fight for equal pay.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/05/alex-morgan-retires-from-professional-soccer-and-is-expecting-her-second-child/"  >(ANNE M. PETERSON, Associated Press, KTLA 5)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 23:35:51 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Fri, 06 Sep 2024 23:35:51 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Eli Ong, WGN 9">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/06/nfl-team-bars-and-where-to-find-them-across-chicago.webp" alt="NFL team bars and where to find them across Chicago" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">NFL team bars and where to find them across Chicago</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      CHICAGO — Are you a football fan who lives in Chicago, but is also from outside the city and roots for a different NFL team besides the Bears? The good news is Chicago has quite a diverse bar scene.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/06/nfl-team-bars-and-where-to-find-them-across-chicago/"  >(Eli Ong, WGN 9)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:30:00 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:30:00 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Kaycee Sloan, WFLA, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/sports/2024/09/05/bucs-set-sights-on-dominant-season-starting-with-opener-against-commanders-in-tampa.webp" alt="Bucs set sights on dominant season starting with opener against Commanders in Tampa" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bucs set sights on dominant season starting with opener against Commanders in Tampa</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Football is finally back and the Tampa Bay Buccaneers are eager to show that last season's success wasn't just a fluke, especially since the team is operating under a new offensive coordinator in Liam Cohen.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/sports/2024/09/05/bucs-set-sights-on-dominant-season-starting-with-opener-against-commanders-in-tampa/"  >(Kaycee Sloan, WFLA, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div></div></fieldset><fieldset><legend><h2>
        <a href="/politics/">Politics News</a>
        </h2></legend>
        <div class="row"><div class="column text"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:06:52 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:06:52 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MORIAH BALINGIT, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/08/walz-touts-democratic-record-of-defending-lgbtq-rights-says-harris-will-advance-cause-if-elected.webp" alt="Walz touts Democratic record of defending LGBTQ+ rights, says Harris will advance cause if elected" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Walz touts Democratic record of defending LGBTQ+ rights, says Harris will advance cause if elected</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz touted Vice President Kamala Harris' record of defending LGBTQ+ rights on Saturday night, pledging to a supportive crowd that she will advance their cause if elected president.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/08/walz-touts-democratic-record-of-defending-lgbtq-rights-says-harris-will-advance-cause-if-elected/"  >(MORIAH BALINGIT, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 16:51:49 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 16:51:49 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="MARC LEVY, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/08/little-debate-that-pennsylvania-is-key-as-harris-and-trump-prep-for-philly-showdown.webp" alt="Little debate that Pennsylvania is key as Harris and Trump prep for Philly showdown" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Little debate that Pennsylvania is key as Harris and Trump prep for Philly showdown</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      HARRISBURG, Pa. (AP) — When Donald Trump and Kamala Harris meet onstage Tuesday night in Philadelphia, they’ll both know there’s little debate that Pennsylvania is critical to their chances of winning the presidency.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/08/little-debate-that-pennsylvania-is-key-as-harris-and-trump-prep-for-philly-showdown/"  >(MARC LEVY, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 12:16:53 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 12:16:53 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="DAN MERICA, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/08/the-ai-industry-uses-a-light-lobbying-touch-to-educate-congress-from-a-corporate-perspective.webp" alt="The AI industry uses a light lobbying touch to educate Congress from a corporate perspective" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">The AI industry uses a light lobbying touch to educate Congress from a corporate perspective</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      WASHINGTON (AP) — The artificial intelligence industry has gone on a lobbying binge in the past few years, deploying scores of hired influencers to help shape potential government action. The growth is not surprising.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/08/the-ai-industry-uses-a-light-lobbying-touch-to-educate-congress-from-a-corporate-perspective/"  >(DAN MERICA, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column hcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:37:57 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:37:57 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Fox News">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/08/sen-john-fetterman-makes-prediction-trump-harris-debate-going-close.webp" alt="Sen. John Fetterman makes prediction for Trump and Harris debate: &#8216;It's going to be close&#8217;" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Sen. John Fetterman makes prediction for Trump and Harris debate: &#8216;It's going to be close&#8217;</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Pennsylvania Sen. John Fetterman on Sunday said he believes that both former President Trump and Vice President Harris will perform well during the upcoming debate.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/08/sen-john-fetterman-makes-prediction-trump-harris-debate-going-close/"  >(Fox News)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 13:21:33 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 13:21:33 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="STEVE KARNOWSKI and MICHAEL GOLDBERG, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/07/takeaways-from-minnesota-gov-tim-walzs-response-to-violence-after-george-floyds-murder.webp" alt="Takeaways from Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz's response to violence after George Floyd's murder" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Takeaways from Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz's response to violence after George Floyd's murder</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      MINNEAPOLIS (AP) — Kamala Harris' selection of Minnesota Gov. Tim Walz to be the Democratic vice presidential candidate has revived the debate over how he handled the biggest crisis of his political career. Minneapolis and St.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/07/takeaways-from-minnesota-gov-tim-walzs-response-to-violence-after-george-floyds-murder/"  >(STEVE KARNOWSKI and MICHAEL GOLDBERG, Associated Press, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:06:12 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Mon, 09 Sep 2024 03:06:12 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Texas Tribune, By Matthew Choi, KPRC 2">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/09/austin-congressman-leads-gop-rebuke-of-biden-administrations-afghanistan-withdrawal.webp" alt="Austin congressman leads GOP rebuke of Biden administration&#8217;s Afghanistan withdrawal" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Austin congressman leads GOP rebuke of Biden administration&#8217;s Afghanistan withdrawal</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      The House Foreign Affairs Committee, which U.S Rep. Michael McCaul chairs, accused Biden of ignoring warnings from his staffers and allies, leaving American interests vulnerable to the Taliban takeover.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/09/austin-congressman-leads-gop-rebuke-of-biden-administrations-afghanistan-withdrawal/"  >(Texas Tribune, By Matthew Choi, KPRC 2)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
</div><div class="column vcwi"><div itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle" class="card">
  <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:06:29 GMT">
  <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="Sat, 07 Sep 2024 17:06:29 GMT">
  <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person">
    <meta itemprop="name" content="Alex Gangitano, KGET 17, NBC">
  </span>
  <div class="card-content">
    <div class="image" role="presentation">
      <img src="/static9/politics/2024/09/07/biden-charts-course-for-final-months-of-presidency.webp" alt="Biden charts course for final months of presidency" itemprop="image" width="400" height="225"
        onerror="this.parentNode.style.display='none'" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" loading="lazy">
    </div>
    <h3 itemprop="headline">Biden charts course for final months of presidency</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      President Biden is charting a course for his final 135 days in office, ramping up his public appearances as he seeks to cement his legacy and support Vice President Harris’s White House bid.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/politics/2024/09/07/biden-charts-course-for-final-months-of-presidency/"  >(Alex Gangitano, KGET 17, NBC)</a>
    </p>
  </div>
